        &lt;br&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Today is the birthday of one of my teachers. Without meeting him, I might not know what I want to be. Everytime I think of him, it reminds me of my family. It reminds me to live a simple life like him. It also reminds me to give my time and energy to people without any reason.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Happy birthday  🔔 🍰🎵&lt;/p&gt;
